Title: Add Unit Tests for DDD Services
Description:
Summary
Added comprehensive JUnit 5 unit test coverage for the DDD Case Management Services application (ddd-services).
Test Coverage Added

Security & Config — SecurityConfig, ServletInitializer, JacksonConfiguration
Services — CaseService, CacheService, EmailService, ReferenceDataService, ADSearchService, AuthenticationService
API Controllers — CaseApiController, CacheApiController, ReferenceApiController, UserController
Repository — CDWRepository, CaseSpecifications
Models — ArrestInfo, CaseFilter, ReferenceCode
Entities — DddCase, AdaList, CategoryList, StatusList, TagList, ItemList, CaseNote, CaseItem, CaseUpload, CaseTag
Converters — LocalDateToDate, DateToLocalDate, TimestampToOffsetDateTime
Exceptions — GlobalExceptionHandler, CaseAccessException, SealedAccessException, FileUploadException
Actuator — BuildInfoHealthIndicator

Tech Stack

JUnit 5 (Jupiter)
Mockito 5.17.0
AssertJ
Spring Boot Test (@WebMvcTest, @ExtendWith)

Total Coverage

40 test files
~1,477 test cases

Notes

Security filter chain excluded from controller tests via @AutoConfigureMockMvc(addFilters = false)
@MockitoSettings(strictness = Strictness.LENIENT) applied where needed for lenient stubbing
SonarQube exclusions configured in pom.xml for Swagger-generated classes
